COMPLIANCE NOTES
================================================================================

1. All third-party licenses are preserved in node_modules at install time.
2. When distributing SAR Manager, this LICENSES file must be retained.
3. No warranty is provided for any third-party components.
4. For use outside of SEASAR, ensure compliance with each component's license.
5. OSRM public demo server is subject to fair-use limits. Consider a dedicated
   routing service for high-volume production use.
6. Azure AD integration requires a registered Azure app in the SEASAR tenant.
   Credentials (client ID, tenant ID) are configured in environment variables,
   not stored in this repository.

